room_title: Escape room "Wonderland" by Escape Cedar Valley in Cedar Falls
room_address: 115 E 4th Street, Suite 101 Cedar Falls, IA 50613
room_description: The white rabbit is in great peril and needs your help! The Red Queen has stolen his pocket watch and banished him to the outer lands. He cannot come back unless his watch is found and returned safely to him in time! Your mission is to travel into his rabbit hole and journey through Wonderland to find his watch within an hour. But be careful - these worlds can be deceiving and sometimes nothing makes sense. Can you unravel the mystery in time? The rabbit is counting on you!
